name: Marker
desc:
Represents a marker on the map.
A marker is an icon placed at a particular point on the map's surface.
The marker can be styled with an image, title, and snippet.

name: Marker
desc:
The marker must have a valid imagePath and latLng.
The width and height must be both provided or both null.

name: imagePath
desc: The image path of the marker, allow only image in png, jpeg, jpg format

name: values
desc: A constant List of the values in this enum, in order of their declaration.

name: Polygon
desc:
Represents a polygon on the map.
A polygon is a closed shape consisting of a set of points, where line segments are drawn between consecutive points.
The polygon can be styled with a fill color, stroke color, and alpha value.
The polygon can also have holes, which are smaller polygons inside the main polygon.

name: Polygon
desc:
Each polygon must have at least three points.
Each hole must have at least three points.

name: Polyline
desc:
Represents a polyline on the map.
A polyline is a list of points, where line segments are drawn between consecutive points.
The polyline can be styled with a color, width, and alpha value.

name: Polyline
desc: Each polyline must have at least two points.

name: VietmapAutomotiveFlutter
desc:
A class that provides the Vietmap Automotive Flutter API.
This class is used to interact with the map on Android Auto and Apple CarPlay.

name: VietmapAutomotiveFlutter
desc:
Constructs a VietmapAutomotiveFlutter.
onMapReady is called when the map is ready to be used.
onMapClick is called when the map is clicked.
onMapRendered is called when the map is rendered.
onStyleLoaded is called when the style is loaded.

name: addMapClickListener
desc: Adds a listener to the map click event.

name: addMapReadyListener
desc: Adds a listener to the map ready event.

name: addMapRenderedListener
desc: Adds a listener to the map rendered event.

name: addMarkers
desc:
Add markers to the map view on Android Auto and Apple CarPlay.
Returns a List of Marker containing the added markers.
or empty list if the markers are not added successfully.

name: addPolygons
desc:
Add polygons to the map view on Android Auto and Apple CarPlay.
Returns a List of Polygon containing the added polygons.
or empty list if the polygons are not added successfully.

name: addPolylines
desc:
Add polylines to the map view on Android Auto and Apple CarPlay.
Returns a List of Polyline containing the added polylines.
or empty list if the polylines are not added successfully.

name: addStyleLoadedListener
desc: Adds a listener to the style loaded event.

name: initAutomotive
desc:
Initializes the map on Android Auto and Apple CarPlay with the given styleUrl and vietMapAPIKey.
Returns a String containing the result of the initialization.
car_app_initialized is returned if the map is initialized successfully.
or null if the map is not initialized successfully.
